  <abstract>This is a point dataset which records relative heights from the field visit survey in West Karawang.


Nearby river name: Cibeet
Basin Name: Citarum

Field metadata:

- agriculture_relative_height: distance to the surface of rice paddies lands, measured from the top of the nearby road. It is negative because these surface were always below the road
- flood_relative_depth: Depth of flood in 2010 West Karawang, as reported by villagers. This depth was measured from the top of the nearby road</abstract>
